nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE MOVING OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC... ...LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH EXPECTED...
summary: ...HENRIETTE MOVING OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC... ...LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH EXPECTED... As of 5:00 AM HST Tue Aug 05 the center of Henriette was located near 16.4, -124.3 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
